data.description:
Fantastic 4BR, two car garage, plus paved driveway to an RV gate in Palm Valley!  With approximately 1,898 sf, this home features matching tile floors throughout, great floor plan that creates great flow and captures lots of natural light.   
Enter the home by walking into the formal living/dining rooms, and given the floor plan, these rooms can be used to fit your family lifestyle.  
The double doors off of the formal areas, are the entrance to the den/office/4th bedroom, which is perfect for use as a bedroom or as a space to work remotely!    
The large master bedroom has windows to the backyard and an ensuite bathroom room with both a tub, shower and double sink vanity.  The master bedroom also has a large walk in closet.   
Two other bedrooms are located adjacent to the master bedroom.  Western views from the bedrooms include fabulous mountain views.   
But the heart of the home is the great room, anchored by the fireplace and high ceiling.  With a large open concept room, the kitchen and breakfast nook are located in the same space. The kitchen features white cabinets and stainless appliances and an island/eat-in bar.
The laundry room serves as a "mud room" into the 2 car garage.
